race.comment: CHICKEN LEGS (2) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start when he made late ground but found a couple better when third over 1000m at Tamworth. Best figures measure up. Go close. LOUD (9) progressed nicely last start to finish a close third over 1200m at Parkes after missing the placings at the previous appearance. Has her share of talent. Hard to beat in this suitable race. SEEBURG (5) finished out of the money two starts back then ran fifth in a 1000m contest at Dalby eight days ago. Will enjoy the class drop and keep safe. VELOCE METEOR (1) fought hard to win last start and has to be included off the back of that effort.
